       PROGRAM-ID.                     DJL4711.
       AUTHOR.                        하윤희.
       DATE-WRITTEN.                   12/09/05.

      *=================================================================
       ENVIRONMENT                     DIVISION.
      *=================================================================
       CONFIGURATION                   SECTION.
       SOURCE-COMPUTER.                IBM-Z10.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER.                IBM-Z10.

      *=================================================================
       DATA                            DIVISION.
      *=================================================================
       WORKING-STORAGE                 SECTION.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      * CONSTANT AREA
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       01  CO-AREA.
           03  CO-PGM-ID               PIC  X(008) VALUE 'DJL4711'.
           03  CO-STAT-OK              PIC  X(002) VALUE '00'.
           03  CO-STAT-DUPM            PIC  X(002) VALUE '01'.
           03  CO-STAT-NOTFND          PIC  X(002) VALUE '02'.
           03  CO-STAT-ERROR           PIC  X(002) VALUE '09'.
           03  CO-STAT-ABNORMAL        PIC  X(002) VALUE '98'.
           03  CO-STAT-SYSERROR        PIC  X(002) VALUE '99'.

           03  CO-CHA-01               PIC  X(002) VALUE '01'.

           03  CO-B3900001             PIC  X(008) VALUE 'B3900001'.
           03  CO-UKJL0036             PIC  X(008) VALUE 'UKJL0036'.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      * WORKING AREA
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WK-AREA.
           03  WK-I                    PIC S9(004) COMP.
           03  WK-NEXT-KEY.
               05 WK-GRNTY-INSTI-NO    PIC  X(013).
               05 WK-TE-GRNTY-INSTI-CD PIC  X(003).

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      * PGM INTERFACE PARAMETER
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       01  XQJL0711-CA.
           COPY  XQJL0711.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      * TABLE INTERFACE PARAMETER
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      * DBIO SQLIO INTERFACE PARAMETER
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
           COPY    YCDBSQLA.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE                         SECTION.
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------

       01  YCCOMMON-CA.
           COPY  YCCOMMON.

       01  XDJL4711-CA.
           COPY  XDJL4711.


      *=================================================================
       PROCEDURE                       DIVISION
                                       USING       YCCOMMON-CA
                                                   XDJL4711-CA
                                                   .
      *=================================================================

      *------------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  처리메인
      *------------------------------------------------------------------
       S0000-MAIN-RTN.

      *@  초기화
           PERFORM S1000-INITIALIZE-RTN
              THRU S1000-INITIALIZE-EXT

      *@  입력값　CHECK
           PERFORM S2000-VALIDATION-RTN
              THRU S2000-VALIDATION-EXT

      *@  업무처리
           PERFORM S3000-PROCESS-RTN
              THRU S3000-PROCESS-EXT

      *@  처리종료
           PERFORM S9000-FINAL-RTN
              THRU S9000-FINAL-EXT
           .
       S0000-MAIN-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *------------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  초기화
      *------------------------------------------------------------------
       S1000-INITIALIZE-RTN.
           INITIALIZE       WK-AREA
                            XDJL4711-OUT
                            XDJL4711-RETURN
      *@DBIO, SQLIO PARAMETER 초기화
                            YCDBSQLA-CA
                            .
       S1000-INITIALIZE-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *------------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  입력값검증
      *------------------------------------------------------------------
       S2000-VALIDATION-RTN.
       S2000-VALIDATION-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *------------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  업무처리
      *------------------------------------------------------------------
       S3000-PROCESS-RTN.

      *@  신용공여관련기관정보(THKJL0071)원장 조회

           EVALUATE XDJL4711-I-PRCSS-DSTIC

           WHEN CO-CHA-01

               INITIALIZE       XQJL0711-IN

      *       그룹회사코드
               MOVE  BICOM-GROUP-CO-CD
                 TO  XQJL0711-I-GROUP-CO-CD
      *       기준년월
               MOVE  XDJL4711-I-BASE-YM
                 TO  XQJL0711-I-BASE-YM

      *       보증기관번호
               MOVE  XDJL4711-I-GRNTY-INSTI-NO
                 TO  XQJL0711-I-GRNTY-INSTI-NO

      *       중단거래여부 확인
               IF  BICOM-DSCN-TRAN-DSTCD = '1' OR '2'

                   MOVE BOCOM-BF-TDK-INFO-CTNT
                     TO WK-NEXT-KEY

      *            N보증기관번호
                   MOVE WK-GRNTY-INSTI-NO
                     TO XQJL0711-I-N-GRNTY-INSTI-NO
      *            NTE보증기관코드
                   MOVE WK-TE-GRNTY-INSTI-CD
                     TO XQJL0711-I-N-TE-GRNTY-INSTI-CD
               END-IF

               #DYSQLA QJL0711 SELECT XQJL0711-CA
      *@1.1 조회결과확인
      *@처리내용 : IF 조회 error 이면 에러처리
               EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-OK
      *@          조회자료MOVE
                   PERFORM S3100-ARRAY-DATA-MOVE-RTN
                      THRU S3100-ARRAY-DATA-MOVE-EXT
               WHEN COND-DBSQL-MRNF
                   #OKEXIT  CO-STAT-NOTFND
               WHEN OTHER
      *           원장에러일경우　에러처리
                   #ERROR CO-B3900001 CO-UKJL0036 CO-STAT-ERROR
               END-EVALUATE
           END-EVALUATE

                        .
       S3000-PROCESS-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  다건조회 출력데이터 조립
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3100-ARRAY-DATA-MOVE-RTN.

      *@  출력파라미터 조립
           PERFORM VARYING WK-I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WK-I > 100
                        OR WK-I > DBSQL-SELECT-CNT
      *        총라인수
               MOVE  WK-I
                 TO  XDJL4711-O-TOTAL-LINE-CNT

      *        보증기관번호
               MOVE  XQJL0711-O-GRNTY-INSTI-NO(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4711-O-GRNTY-INSTI-NO(WK-I)

      *        TE보증기관코드
               MOVE  XQJL0711-O-T-E-GRNTY-INSTI-CD(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4711-O-T-E-GRNTY-INSTI-CD(WK-I)

      *        보증기관명
               MOVE  XQJL0711-O-GRNTY-INSTI-NAME(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4711-O-GRNTY-INSTI-NAME(WK-I)

      *        신표준산업분류코드
               MOVE  XQJL0711-O-NEW-SI-CLSFI-CD(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4711-O-NEW-SI-CLSFI-CD(WK-I)

      *        국가코드
               MOVE  XQJL0711-O-NATNL-CD(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4711-O-NATNL-CD(WK-I)

      *        신용공여위험가중치
               MOVE  XQJL0711-O-GRCR-RISK-WGHT(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4711-O-GRCR-RISK-WGHT(WK-I)

      *        신용공여기관구분
               MOVE  XQJL0711-O-GRCR-INSTI-DSTCD(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4711-O-GRCR-INSTI-DSTCD(WK-I)

      *        보증기관고객식별자
               MOVE  XQJL0711-O-GRNTY-I-CUST-IDNFR(WK-I)
                 TO  XDJL4711-O-GRNTY-I-CUST-IDNFR(WK-I)

           END-PERFORM

           IF  DBSQL-SELECT-CNT > 100
      *        N보증기관번호
               MOVE XQJL0711-O-GRNTY-INSTI-NO(WK-I)
                 TO WK-GRNTY-INSTI-NO
      *        NTE보증기관코드
               MOVE XQJL0711-O-T-E-GRNTY-INSTI-CD(WK-I)
                 TO WK-TE-GRNTY-INSTI-CD

               #DSCNTR 2 WK-NEXT-KEY
           END-IF

                                .
       S3100-ARRAY-DATA-MOVE-EXT.
           EXIT.


      *------------------------------------------------------------------
      *@  처리종료
      *------------------------------------------------------------------
       S9000-FINAL-RTN.
           #OKEXIT  CO-STAT-OK.
       S9000-FINAL-EXT.
           EXIT.
